= Abstract

:hardbreaks: ;
:nofooter:
:icons: font
:linkattrs:
:imagesdir: ./../media/

NetApp HCI with Anthos is a verified, best-practice hybrid cloud architecture for the deployment of an on-premises Google Kubernetes Engine environment in a reliable and dependable manner. This architecture reference document provides design and deployment validation of the Anthos solution on NetApp HCI and a use-case validation of the deployment.
